title: MBMBaM 372: Face 2 Face: Sock-Based Target Crimes
description: Here's another one of our live shows from our recent tour of America's most Northeastern reaches -- this time from the Wilbur in Boston! This was our first of two shows that night, which is good, because this is before things went way, way off the rails.
author: shows@mbmbam.com (Justin McElroy)
